snippet.title: Turok 2 Teaser (cancelled)
snippet.description:
Made by the animator (Jeremy Brown) who worked on Turok, a live-action teaser of the cancelled Turok 2.
Bring back Turok! It seems to just be for the fun of it that he made this and posted rather then any news. 

Jeremy Browns Vimeo post: https://vimeo.com/130049705
http://www.rattlesnakefilms.ca/
